  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyodorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "ソロのお仕事もレッスンもお休みにさせてもらって……\n{user}さんには感謝しないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for letting me take a break from my solo work and lessons…\nI have to thank {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.3008793592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "千紗もありがとう。気分転換に付き合ってくれて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you too‚ Chisa. For coming with me to take my mind off things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、大変なのは分かってるから。それに最近は\nいろいろあって一緒に出かけられなかったでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No problem‚ I know you’re going through a lot. And we haven’t been\nable to go out lately because of everything that’s been going on‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.444059213
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "だから今日は、一杯遊ぼう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So let’s have some fun today‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.444059213,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.9364627441
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "千紗……そうね。一杯遊ぼっか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa… You’re right. Let’s have some fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.9364627441,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.9197960775
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.9197960775
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 29.1697960775
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "ご飯、美味しかったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The food was good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.9697960775,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.4217234057
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。お店の雰囲気も良かったし、また今度……\nあ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was. The atmosphere of the restaurant was nice too‚ so next time…\nAh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.6997678496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.4883885465
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "あの大型ビジョンに映ってるのって\n最近凄く勢いがあるアイドルグループだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That idol group on the big screen…\nThey’re really popular lately‚ aren’t they?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.3348426651,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.6150096975
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。新しいミュージックビデオみたいだけど……\nかっこいいし、雰囲気も凄く出てるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. It looks like a new music video…\nIt’s cool‚ and the vibe is really great.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.0059934708,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.7150096975
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "あのステップ、月ストに応用したらいい感じに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we apply those steps to Moon Tempest‚ it would be great…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.7150096975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.5816761099
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "ご、ごめんね、千紗\nこれじゃ気分転換の意味がないわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Sorry‚ Chisa.\nThis isn’t helping me take my mind off things at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.9816761099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.9483427766
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃん……\n今はそれでいいんじゃないかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Big sis…\nI think it’s okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.3666664124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.3242157701
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "え……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.3242157701,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.6242137356
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "今悩んでるのは、月ストのことでしょ？\nずっと頑張ってきた、大切なグループのことだし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What you’re worried about now is Moon Tempest‚ right?\nIt’s a group you’ve worked so hard for‚ a group that’s precious to you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.0333310445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.8033976002
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "無理に考えないようにすると\nかえって辛くなっちゃうと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you try to force yourself not to think about it‚\nI think it’ll just make you feel worse.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.6666643779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tears-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 86.2065494939
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.2065494939
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "そう……ね。本当に毎日月ストのことばかり\n考えていたから、いきなり忘れるのは無理があるかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re… right. I've really been thinking about Moon Tempest every day‚\nso it’s probably impossible for me to suddenly forget about them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.3333330791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.9732161605
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "うん、そうだと思う\n私もサニピのこと、毎日考えてるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I think so.\nI think about Sunny Peace every day too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.1333310445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "だから、今は……ぐるぐる悩んじゃうのは\nしょうがない、って思ったらどうかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ how about you just accept that\nit’s okay to be lost in thought for now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.9333269755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.9742044533
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "私はいくらでも、お姉ちゃんのお話、聞きたいから\n悩みでもなんでも、いつでも話してね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m always willing to listen to you.\nWhether it’s worries or anything else‚ you can talk to me anytime.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.0333218892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.7332490052
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "千紗……っ\nありがとう……千紗がいてくれて良かった……っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa…!\nThank you… I’m glad I have you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.9999156719,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.1999156719
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_03-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ……\nお姉ちゃん、大丈夫だよ。いつでも私がそばにいるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe…\nIt’s okay‚ big sis. I’m always here for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.7333193461,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.5333193461
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.5095132595
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.5095132595
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_outside-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 134.7595132595
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
